【Multiport Charging】: The charger block has Dual USB-C ports and Dual USB-A ports. Allow users to charge phone, tablet and headphones simultaneously to minimize waiting time. It’s also a great space saver instead of taking up 4 wall outlet ports. The best replacement for your original usb charger.

【Universal Compatibility】:Due to the special 4-port,the USB charger is compatible with almost all electronic devices,charging adapter for iPhone 15/15 Pro /15 Pro Max/14/14 Pro/14 Pro Max/13/13 Mini/13 Pro Max/12/12 Pro Max/12 Pro Max/12 Mini/SE 2020/11/11 Pro/11 Pro Max/XR/XS/X/8/7,iPad Air/Pro/Mini,Samsung Galaxy S22/S21/S20/S10/S9/S8/A12/A13/A22/A32/A52/A53/A71/Note 20 10,Tablets,LG,Motorola,Google Pixel and other digital devices compatible.

【Compact & Portable】: Incredibly compact size for enhanced portability.All this power comes installed in a pocket-friendly compact body, to go wherever the journey takes you. Ideal for home, office and on the go.
【Safe & Reliable】: Equipped with a smart chip, which can adjust the input power of the phone to prevent the phone from overcharging and overheating.
